Title: Malaika Arora clicked in the Bandra
Narrative:
Malaika Arora was photographed in Mumbai‘s Bandra suburb today. Malaika Arora who popped in neon. The fitness diva, who also runs a yoga business, was snapped exiting her yoga space with Aakansha Ranjan. 
Malaika was snapped in a pair of neon shorts and a grey full-sleeved jacket.
